[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    390[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m1[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mEnrollment briefing for the care manager.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m A structured-output prompt takes the patient's clinical context, the recommended program, the per-program uplift estimates with confidence intervals, recent clinical events, and the suspected barriers, and returns a one-paragraph briefing the care manager reads before initial outreach. Includes "what to lead with," "anticipated concerns," and "social context that matters."[K
