[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    401[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    402[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mAmazon Connect (or contracted outreach platform) for care-manager telephonic outreach.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m Care management programs are predominantly telephonic and televisit. Plans with in-house care management teams often build on Amazon Connect; plans with vendor care management use the vendor's queue and a structured-event integration. The AWS-specific piece is HIPAA-eligible call recording, the contact-flow-to-engagement-event integration, and the per-care-manager work-queue routing that respects language, condition, and program-specialization match.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    403[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    404[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mAmazon SES for member-facing email and Pinpoint (or contracted vendor) for SMS.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m Same as prior chapters; both under BAA. [38;2;101;115;126m<!--[38;2;101;115;126m TODO: confirm SES HIPAA eligibility and BAA scope at the time of build; verify Pinpoint SMS eligibility. [38;2;101;115;126m-->[K
